      prompt: `The cost of renting a piece of construction equipment for up to 10 days is $330 for the first day and $165 for each additional day. Which of the following equations gives the cost <em>y</em>, in dollars, of renting the equipment for <em>x</em> days, where <em>x</em> is a positive integer and <em>x</em> ≤ 10?`,
